"{\"uid\": \"dailypost.ng-2024-08-12-olympics-nigerian-only-participated-in-sports-that-dont-need-investment-seun-kuti\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Published  on  By  Famous singer, Seun Kuti has blasted the Nigerian government for not investing in sports.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 108, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 34, \"end\": 43, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seun_Kuti\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Seun Kuti\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seun_Kuti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seun_Kuti\"}, {\"begin\": 60, \"end\": 79, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Federal_government_of_Nigeria\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nigerian government\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Federal_government_of_Nigeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Federal_government_of_Nigeria\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a viral video on social media, Seun reacted to team Nigeria's poor performance at the just concluded 2024 Olympics in Paris.\", \"from\": 110, \"to\": 237, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 165, \"end\": 172, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"score\": 0.9999999968708835, \"rank\": 3.1290734288253303e-09, \"text\": \"Nigeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\"}, {\"begin\": 231, \"end\": 236, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999991794282961, \"rank\": 8.205724557680402e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While highlighting the 2024 Olympics, the singer revealed that Nigeria only participated in sporting events that do not require investment.\", \"from\": 239, \"to\": 378, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 302, \"end\": 309, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"score\": 0.9999999968708835, \"rank\": 3.1290734288253303e-09, \"text\": \"Nigeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I watched the Olympic games.\", \"from\": 380, \"to\": 409, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"look at how poorly we performed.\", \"from\": 410, \"to\": 442, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"How many sports are we competing in?\", \"from\": 443, \"to\": 479, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I saw that it was only sports that did not need investment that Nigerians participated in.\", \"from\": 480, \"to\": 570, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We only did sports that needed minimum investment.\", \"from\": 571, \"to\": 621, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You know, to play football, you need a ball, post and net and in some places, boys would use slippers to create a goalpost.\", \"from\": 623, \"to\": 747, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But in sports that need things like rackets, basketball courts, rims and nets where you can not easily improvise, we were not there.\", \"from\": 748, \"to\": 880, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We competed in track and field events because it is easy to do running.\", \"from\": 881, \"to\": 952, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But we are never in sports that need equipment.\", \"from\": 953, \"to\": 1000, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Nigerians know all these sports and bet on them so how much would it take to create a good league and gift the winners 25 million dollars?\", \"from\": 1002, \"to\": 1141, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Let there be a minimum of a million dollars per year, after all, this is what boys are earning in Europe.\", \"from\": 1142, \"to\": 1247, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Nigerians are unable to enjoy their children's talents, all our big superstars.\", \"from\": 1249, \"to\": 1329, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Which other shows do they play in Nigeria?\", \"from\": 1330, \"to\": 1372, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1364, \"end\": 1371, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"score\": 0.9999999968708835, \"rank\": 3.1290734288253303e-09, \"text\": \"Nigeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was watching the Olympics and I saw a lot of people with Nigerian sounding names doing incredible things for other countries.\", \"from\": 1373, \"to\": 1500, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1432, \"end\": 1440, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigerians\", \"score\": 0.9999889810005707, \"rank\": 1.101412721762543e-05, \"text\": \"Nigerian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigerians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigerians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If Simone Biles can be that great, imagine how many talents that are wasting away because people will not invest in gymnastics and train our children.\\\"\", \"from\": 1501, \"to\": 1652, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1504, \"end\": 1516, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Simone Biles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\"}, {\"begin\": 1617, \"end\": 1627, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gymnastics\", \"score\": 0.9996559840650268, \"rank\": 0.00034106113199531125, \"text\": \"gymnastics\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gymnastics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gymnastics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Video:  \\\"Na only the sports wey no need investment na im Nigeria dey\\\"  - Seun Kutipic.twitter.com/az8bxT2je3  - @ (@OneJoblessBoy)August 10, 2024    EndBadGovernance: Address d